song_lyrics: Sahajānand Hari, bhajī lyone Sahajānand Hari... °ṭek
Dārū māṭī chorī averī, e chāreno tyāg karī... Bhajī° 1
Janma maraṇnu sankaṭ moṭu, te thakī manmā ḍarī... Bhajī° 2
Nārāyaṇnu nām ja letn, bhavjaḷ jāsho tarī... Bhajī° 3
Niṣhkuḷānand kahe nishank thaīne, mānjo vāt kharī... Bhajī° 4
title: Sahajānand Hari bhajī lyone Sahajānand Hari
